00:34:41.284 --> 00:34:44.203
-What are we doing here?
-I'm getting something to eat.

508
00:34:44.245 --> 00:34:47.498
You want anything.
like a Cup O'Noodles?

509
00:34:47.540 --> 00:34:51.627
Carter. stop wasting my time.
I made a promise to Soo Yung.

510
00:34:51.668 --> 00:34:54.087
You're right.
I have been wasting your time.

511
00:34:54.087 --> 00:34:56.923
I'm sorry. Just let me
go get something to eat.

512
00:34:56.965 --> 00:34:59.217
When I come back out. I'll take
you wherever you want to go.

513
00:35:01.427 --> 00:35:02.553
Shake on it?

514
00:35:04.555 --> 00:35:06.223
Hey. what are you doing?

515
00:35:06.265 --> 00:35:09.101
You ain't the only one
with quick hands. are you?

516
00:35:09.101 --> 00:35:10.728
I'll be right back.

517
00:35:17.776 --> 00:35:20.778
Hey. man. I got you
a beef-and-bean burrito.

518
00:35:33.415 --> 00:35:35.125
We have a taxicab approaching.

519
00:35:35.167 --> 00:35:39.254
A man stepping out--Asian.
About 5'10".

520
00:35:39.295 --> 00:35:41.089
We've got someone
approaching the gate.

521
00:35:41.130 --> 00:35:42.465
Dropped off by a cab.

522
00:35:46.469 --> 00:35:47.928
Tell them to intercept.

523
00:35:47.970 --> 00:35:49.138
Intercept.

524
00:35:49.179 --> 00:35:50.806
We will intercept.

525
00:35:56.311 --> 00:35:57.771
Can I help you?

526
00:35:57.812 --> 00:36:00.565
-Yes. I must see the consul.
-About what?

527
00:36:00.607 --> 00:36:02.900
Please. it's very important.

528
00:36:02.942 --> 00:36:06.028
Why don't you tell us
why you need to see the consul?

529
00:36:06.070 --> 00:36:07.571
We'll tell you
whether it's important.

530
00:36:07.613 --> 00:36:09.657
Do you have identification?

531
00:36:10.741 --> 00:36:12.659
It's about his daughter
Soo Yung.

532
00:36:12.701 --> 00:36:14.161
Hands above your head!

533
00:36:14.202 --> 00:36:15.620
He asked about
the consul's daughter.

534
00:36:15.662 --> 00:36:16.788
He asked about the daughter.

535
00:36:16.830 --> 00:36:18.665
You don't understand.
I was invited.

536
00:36:23.753 --> 00:36:25.755
Don't move! Throw your gun away.

537
00:36:25.796 --> 00:36:29.049
-He's gonna kill them.
-Is everything all right?

538
00:36:29.091 --> 00:36:31.051
You'll be safer
on the second floor.

539
00:36:31.093 --> 00:36:33.136
I'm sorry.

540
00:36:33.178 --> 00:36:34.971
I'm sorry about this.

541
00:36:56.116 --> 00:36:57.742
He went over.

542
00:36:57.784 --> 00:36:58.952
Let's go!

543
00:37:00.328 --> 00:37:02.705
He's on the grounds! Come on!

544
00:37:32.858 --> 00:37:34.735
Stay away from the window.
please.

545
00:37:34.735 --> 00:37:35.902
Right here.

546
00:37:41.741 --> 00:37:43.076
Get down! Now!

547
00:37:57.756 --> 00:37:58.923
Don't move!

548
00:38:12.311 --> 00:38:15.188
I think there has been
a misunderstanding.

549
00:38:15.230 --> 00:38:17.190
It's all right. It's OK.

550
00:38:17.232 --> 00:38:19.901
It's him. The guy from China.

551
00:38:19.943 --> 00:38:21.653
What?

552
00:38:21.694 --> 00:38:23.571
Come in. please.

553
00:38:27.741 --> 00:38:32.412
Mr. Russ. I would like you
to meet Detective inspector Lee.

554
00:38:32.454 --> 00:38:34.331
Excuse me very much.

555
00:38:37.500 --> 00:38:38.752
Your gun.

556
00:38:43.423 --> 00:38:45.591
Where the hell is Carter?

557
00:38:52.764 --> 00:38:54.808
Then I gotta put up with this.

558
00:38:56.601 --> 00:38:58.728
Seen a little Asian dude
about this height...

559
00:38:58.770 --> 00:39:00.522
with a steering wheel
on his arm?

560
00:39:00.563 --> 00:39:02.482
Go screw yourself.

561
00:39:02.482 --> 00:39:04.400
What you say?

562
00:39:04.442 --> 00:39:05.818
I said go screw yourself.

563
00:39:05.860 --> 00:39:08.737
You take your sensitive ass
up there and let me in!

564
00:39:08.779 --> 00:39:10.656
Don't make me get up
out of this truck!

565
00:39:10.698 --> 00:39:11.949
Let this putz in.

566
00:39:11.990 --> 00:39:14.493
Man. when I get up in here.
I'm slapping somebody.

567
00:39:15.202 --> 00:39:16.661
What happened. Carter?

568
00:39:16.703 --> 00:39:18.788
I ain't supposed to be
jumping on buses!

569
00:39:18.830 --> 00:39:21.666
I do not do that!
I am not Carl Lewis!

570
00:39:21.708 --> 00:39:23.459
Who is this man?

571
00:39:24.252 --> 00:39:25.670
Sir. I can explain.

572
00:39:25.711 --> 00:39:28.172
Agent Carter has been helping
with my investigation.

573
00:39:28.214 --> 00:39:31.091
He's upset that we have not
done our job.

574
00:39:31.133 --> 00:39:34.136
Me and Lee are taking care
of the situation.

575
00:39:34.177 --> 00:39:36.346
We have everything
under control.

576
00:39:36.388 --> 00:39:38.139
We'll get your daughter back
safe and sound.

577
00:39:38.181 --> 00:39:40.892
He is very passionate
about finding your daughter.

578
00:39:40.934 --> 00:39:43.186
Well. I owe you my gratitude.

579
00:39:43.227 --> 00:39:46.689
We wanted Detective Lee to have
one of our best men by his side.

580
00:39:46.731 --> 00:39:48.691
Agent Russ.
maybe this is a good time...

581
00:39:48.732 --> 00:39:50.818
to tell him
the details of my assignment.

582
00:39:53.237 --> 00:39:55.197
Can I speak to you
for a moment?

583
00:39:55.238 --> 00:39:56.990
You wanna speak to me?
For a moment?

584
00:39:57.032 --> 00:39:58.241
In private?

585
00:39:59.742 --> 00:40:03.371
Oh. I see!
This must be G-14 classified.

586
00:40:03.413 --> 00:40:04.956
FBI-type stuff.

587
00:40:04.997 --> 00:40:08.709
Let me call my captain
and let him know what going on.

588
00:40:08.751 --> 00:40:13.046
We'll talk in a second.
When a G-14 comes around.

589
00:40:13.088 --> 00:40:14.256
Who's this? Hello?

590
00:40:14.297 --> 00:40:16.341
Am I speaking with FBI?

591
00:40:16.383 --> 00:40:19.219
-Give me the phone.
-Yeah. this is the FBI.

592
00:40:19.260 --> 00:40:21.012
You are FBI?

593
00:40:21.054 --> 00:40:22.722
Yeah. this is the FBI.

594
00:40:22.764 --> 00:40:26.225
If you want the girl back alive.
listen and do not talk.

595
00:40:26.267 --> 00:40:27.768
OK. I'm listening.
Let me get a pen.

596
00:40:28.769 --> 00:40:30.229
All right. Cool.

597
00:40:30.270 --> 00:40:33.565
The drop will be made tonight.
11:00 p.m.

598
00:40:33.607 --> 00:40:36.109
The amount will be $50 million.

599
00:40:36.151 --> 00:40:37.736
Fifty million dollars?

600
00:40:37.777 --> 00:40:40.488
Who you think you kidnapped.
Chelsea Clinton?

601
00:40:40.530 --> 00:40:41.739
Keep him talking.

602
00:40:41.781 --> 00:40:44.242
In used currency.
Nothing bigger than a 50.

603
00:40:44.283 --> 00:40:47.328
All right. Cool.
Fifty million. No problem.

604
00:40:47.369 --> 00:40:50.581
I want 20 million in 50s...

605
00:40:50.622 --> 00:40:52.124
Twenty million in 50s.

606
00:40:52.166 --> 00:40:54.292
Twenty million in 20s...

607
00:40:54.334 --> 00:40:55.794
Twenty million in 20s.

608
00:40:55.836 --> 00:40:57.921
And 10 million in 10s.

609
00:40:57.963 --> 00:40:59.756
Ten million in 10s.

610
00:40:59.798 --> 00:41:01.591
You want any fries with that?

611
00:41:01.633 --> 00:41:03.051
What is your name?

612
00:41:03.092 --> 00:41:05.803
You called us.
Why you want to know my name?

613
00:41:05.845 --> 00:41:08.806
I just want to be able to tell
the consul who is responsible...

614
00:41:08.847 --> 00:41:11.225
for his daughter's death
because he talk too much.

615
00:41:11.266 --> 00:41:13.226
All right. hold up. Calm down.

616
00:41:13.268 --> 00:41:15.687
I'm trying to hook you up.
I'm on your side.

617
00:41:15.729 --> 00:41:17.731
You will receive instructions
for the drop...

618
00:41:17.772 --> 00:41:20.733
half an hour
before it is to be made.

619
00:41:20.775 --> 00:41:23.861
If it is successful.
the girl will live.

620
00:41:23.903 --> 00:41:25.738
I'm gonna make sure
you get the money...

621
00:41:25.780 --> 00:41:27.740
and we can spend it
together when you do...

622
00:41:27.782 --> 00:41:29.950
'cause I don't even
really work for them.

623
00:41:31.285 --> 00:41:33.954
We got it.
620 South Broadway. Downtown.

624
00:41:45.298 --> 00:41:49.760
Team one. proceed down 6th
to 6th and Broadway.

625
00:41:49.802 --> 00:41:53.221
Team two. I want you around
the back on 4th and Main.

626
00:41:53.305 --> 00:41:54.765
Set up a perimeter.

627
00:41:54.806 --> 00:41:57.684
Take your team and cover
the building floor by floor...

628
00:41:57.726 --> 00:41:59.436
all the way to the top. Move.

629
00:42:07.777 --> 00:42:09.236
Two men around back.

630
00:42:09.278 --> 00:42:10.738
They must not go
into the building.

631
00:42:10.779 --> 00:42:13.407
Yeah. you right.
Let's go tell them. Come on.

632
00:42:13.448 --> 00:42:15.117
Take positions on the corner.

633
00:42:17.160 --> 00:42:19.788
Mr. Russ. you must pull
your men back.

634
00:42:19.829 --> 00:42:21.706
What the hell
are you doing here?

635
00:42:21.748 --> 00:42:23.666
Where's Carter?

636
00:42:26.460 --> 00:42:28.254
Please. listen to me.

637
00:42:28.295 --> 00:42:30.756
You may be very competent.
but the mere fact...

638
00:42:30.798 --> 00:42:33.842
that you know this girl
compromises your judgment.

639
00:42:39.013 --> 00:42:42.725
Sir. if you were asking
for $50 million dollars...

640
00:42:42.767 --> 00:42:44.477
would you be in a place
like that?

641
00:42:44.519 --> 00:42:46.645
Get this clown away from me.

642
00:42:46.687 --> 00:42:47.855
Take a hike!

643
00:42:57.489 --> 00:42:58.740
Hey. man.

644
00:42:58.782 --> 00:43:00.074
Why were you hiding?

645
00:43:00.116 --> 00:43:01.659
What you talking about?
I wasn't hiding.

646
00:43:01.701 --> 00:43:02.952
You were hiding.

647
00:43:02.994 --> 00:43:04.996
I bent down to tie my shoe.

648
00:43:05.037 --> 00:43:06.997
Sir. the area is secured.

649
00:43:07.748 --> 00:43:08.707
Room's empty.

650
00:43:08.749 --> 00:43:10.084
Damn it!

651
00:43:28.392 --> 00:43:29.810
Everybody pull back!

652
00:43:29.852 --> 00:43:31.019
Goddamn!

653
00:43:31.061 --> 00:43:33.146
Get some paramedics
down here now!

654
00:43:33.188 --> 00:43:35.023
Evacuate the building
right away!

655
00:43:35.065 --> 00:43:36.525
Get fire crews here!

656
00:43:36.566 --> 00:43:39.360
We got an explosion
at 6th and Broadway.

657
00:44:42.585 --> 00:44:44.712
That ain't far enough. man!

658
00:44:44.754 --> 00:44:47.756
I ain't Kareem Abdul-Jabbar!
Push it down some more!

659
00:45:50.564 --> 00:45:53.108
Carter. don't come any--Stop!

660
00:45:53.150 --> 00:45:55.026
What the hell you--

661
00:46:17.631 --> 00:46:19.841
I think I done broke my shit.

662
00:46:19.883 --> 00:46:22.010
Who was that you was chasing?

663
00:46:22.051 --> 00:46:26.055
His name is Sang from Hong Kong.
Because of you he got away.

664
00:46:26.097 --> 00:46:28.349
Why you ain't tell me
about the bridge?

665
00:46:28.390 --> 00:46:30.809
-I did.
-No. you didn't.

666
00:46:30.851 --> 00:46:32.019
I said stop.

667
00:46:32.060 --> 00:46:33.687
I don't understand
what you be saying.

668
00:46:33.729 --> 00:46:35.355
What?

669
00:46:35.397 --> 00:46:38.108
You see what I'm saying?

670
00:46:38.149 --> 00:46:39.651
What's this in your hand?

671
00:46:39.692 --> 00:46:41.527
He dropped it.

672
00:46:41.569 --> 00:46:42.779
Oh. shit.

673
00:46:42.820 --> 00:46:45.489
-Come on.
-Where are we going?

674
00:46:45.531 --> 00:46:46.907
I messed up my suit.

675
00:46:57.626 --> 00:46:59.377
Fifteen seconds.

676
00:47:05.633 --> 00:47:07.301
Make a decision.

677
00:47:14.433 --> 00:47:15.767
Oh. shit!

678
00:47:17.936 --> 00:47:19.604
Did I come at a bad time?

679
00:47:19.646 --> 00:47:23.066
I got bad news for you. Johnson.
We're all dead.

680
00:47:23.107 --> 00:47:24.942
I was distracted. sir.

681
00:47:24.984 --> 00:47:26.944
Distractions can occur
in the field.

682
00:47:26.986 --> 00:47:28.904
That's why
we call this practice.

683
00:47:28.946 --> 00:47:31.323
If you can't handle
the pressure. then quit.

684
00:47:31.365 --> 00:47:32.574
Yes. sir.

685
00:47:32.616 --> 00:47:35.410
Man. give her a break.
Don't worry about him.

686
00:47:35.452 --> 00:47:38.371
How you doing. girl?
Give me some love.

687
00:47:38.413 --> 00:47:40.039
Why are you tormenting me?

688
00:47:40.081 --> 00:47:41.582
That any way to treat
an old friend?

689
00:47:41.624 --> 00:47:44.752
I came to see how you was doing.
and I need some help.

690
00:47:44.794 --> 00:47:46.587
Help?

691
00:47:46.629 --> 00:47:48.797
I know that you have
strong feelings for me...

692
00:47:48.839 --> 00:47:50.632
but we gotta put that aside.

693
00:47:50.674 --> 00:47:52.342
It's a little girl's life
at stake here.

694
00:47:52.384 --> 00:47:54.803
Since when do care about anybody
but yourself?

695
00:47:54.845 --> 00:47:57.097
Please just take a look at this.

696
00:47:57.138 --> 00:47:59.974
We found this on a kidnapper.
Tell me what this is.

697
00:48:00.016 --> 00:48:03.311
You want me to work with you?
I don't have time for this.

698
00:48:03.352 --> 00:48:05.187
I got enough shit to deal with.

699
00:48:07.148 --> 00:48:08.524
Who are you?

700
00:48:08.566 --> 00:48:11.110
-Sorry we got you in trouble.
-Yeah. he's sorry.

701
00:48:11.151 --> 00:48:12.819
Tell me something
about this I don't know.

702
00:48:12.861 --> 00:48:15.739
A remote. Could be nitro cap.
could be cross-delayed...

703
00:48:15.780 --> 00:48:17.782
definitely not homemade.
definitely not American.

704
00:48:17.824 --> 00:48:21.119
It could open up a garage door.
or blow up some C-4.

705
00:48:21.160 --> 00:48:22.870
C-4?

706
00:48:22.912 --> 00:48:24.455
Yeah. C-4.

707
00:48:26.332 --> 00:48:28.834
This means so much to me.

708
00:48:30.336 --> 00:48:32.838
Hey. and I'm sorry about
spreading all those rumors...

709
00:48:32.880 --> 00:48:34.840
on Christmas about us
sleeping together.

710
00:48:34.840 --> 00:48:36.132
What?!

711
00:48:36.174 --> 00:48:37.634
He's just joking.

712
00:48:44.932 --> 00:48:47.017
Hey. Bobby. what's up. man?

713
00:48:48.519 --> 00:48:52.022
-I need to see Clive Cod.
-No way. Carter.

714
00:48:52.064 --> 00:48:54.024
It's lights out.
They're locked down.

715
00:48:54.066 --> 00:48:55.192
You want me to lose my job?

716
00:48:55.233 --> 00:48:58.862
I got you this damn job.
You better let me in here.

717
00:48:58.903 --> 00:49:00.280
Can't do it.

718
00:49:00.321 --> 00:49:02.949
Didn't I turn my back when
you bought that bag of weed?

719
00:49:02.990 --> 00:49:05.284
I was splitting it with you.

720
00:49:05.326 --> 00:49:06.744
Didn't I give you
the bigger half?

721
00:49:06.786 --> 00:49:08.746
Do me this favor.

722
00:49:10.372 --> 00:49:12.958
Shit. You got five minutes.

723
00:49:13.000 --> 00:49:14.793
Hey. Cod.

724
00:49:14.835 --> 00:49:16.670
Your two brothers
are here to see you.

725
00:49:22.425 --> 00:49:25.511
Clive. how you doing. man?

726
00:49:25.553 --> 00:49:27.596
You got a lot of balls.
coming here.

727
00:49:27.638 --> 00:49:30.641
I was just around the way.
Figured you would be bored.

728
00:49:30.682 --> 00:49:32.893
I came to see how you was doing.

729
00:49:32.935 --> 00:49:34.353
What the hell do you want?

730
00:49:34.394 --> 00:49:36.021
I just came to bring you a gift.

731
00:49:36.062 --> 00:49:39.232
I know you got time to kill.
I brought you a toy.

732
00:49:39.274 --> 00:49:41.109
-I don't want that.
-You don't?

733
00:49:41.150 --> 00:49:43.194
Somebody told me
you like this stuff.

734
00:49:43.236 --> 00:49:46.238
I don't like stuff like that.
I don't even know what it is.

735
00:49:46.280 --> 00:49:47.781
You never sold this to nobody?

736
00:49:47.823 --> 00:49:49.992
How could l.
when I don't know what it is?

737
00:49:50.034 --> 00:49:52.077
-Hold it.
-I don't want to hold it.

738
00:49:52.119 --> 00:49:54.996
-Just touch it.
-I don't want to touch it.

739
00:49:55.038 --> 00:49:57.207
-You scared of it?
-You think I'm stupid?

740
00:49:57.249 --> 00:49:58.375
Stupid enough to get busted.

741
00:49:58.416 --> 00:50:00.501
You want my fingerprints
so you can frame me.

742
00:50:00.543 --> 00:50:02.045
Why would I do something
like that?

743
00:50:02.086 --> 00:50:03.671
Think I would try
tricking you again?

744
00:50:03.713 --> 00:50:05.298
I don't have to frame you.

745
00:50:05.339 --> 00:50:07.800
You'll do life
for killing the little girl.

746
00:50:07.842 --> 00:50:09.468
I don't know anything
about a little girl.

747
00:50:09.510 --> 00:50:12.346
That ain't
what I'll tell everybody.

748
00:50:12.387 --> 00:50:14.056
I don't know anything.

749
00:50:14.097 --> 00:50:15.390
I got a big mouth. Clive.

750
00:50:15.432 --> 00:50:16.600
Let me tell you something.

751
00:50:16.641 --> 00:50:19.644
I don't know anything.
so you can kiss my fat ass.

752
00:50:19.686 --> 00:50:22.105
It'd take me all day
to kiss your fat ass.

753
00:50:22.105 --> 00:50:23.815
You want some of this?

754
00:50:23.856 --> 00:50:25.566
I'll give you all you want.

755
00:50:25.608 --> 00:50:27.151
Give me a name.

756
00:50:27.193 --> 00:50:28.944
I ain't telling you shit.

757
00:50:31.864 --> 00:50:33.490
She's only 11 years old.

758
00:50:33.532 --> 00:50:35.742
I don't want her to die.

759
00:50:35.784 --> 00:50:38.078
Look at the picture.

760
00:50:38.119 --> 00:50:40.205
I don't care about him or you.

761
00:50:40.246 --> 00:50:42.457
