01:31:00.798 --> 01:31:03.759
First class. I like this.
This is tight.

1274
01:31:03.801 --> 01:31:05.177
Can I take your jacket. sir?

1275
01:31:05.219 --> 01:31:08.180
My jacket? No.
You can take this bag. though.

1276
01:31:08.222 --> 01:31:10.182
How you doing? What's up?

1277
01:31:10.224 --> 01:31:11.683
What's up. man?

1278
01:31:11.725 --> 01:31:13.185
-You ready to go?
-Yep.

1279
01:31:13.226 --> 01:31:14.728
May I offer you some peanuts?

1280
01:31:20.525 --> 01:31:22.819
You never told me
you spoke Chinese.

1281
01:31:22.860 --> 01:31:26.280
I never told you I didn't.
You assumed I didn't.

1282
01:31:26.363 --> 01:31:29.366
This is cool. Han's letting me
go to Hong Kong with you.

1283
01:31:29.408 --> 01:31:31.660
I ain't been on no vacation
in five years?

1284
01:31:31.702 --> 01:31:34.788
We can hang in my crib.
I will show you my hood.

1285
01:31:34.830 --> 01:31:37.165
No. you can show me a couple
of them Chinese girls.

1286
01:31:37.207 --> 01:31:39.667
I want a massage.
I'm gonna get buck wild.

1287
01:31:39.709 --> 01:31:44.130
No police work for two weeks?
How long this flight?

1288
01:31:44.171 --> 01:31:46.841
-Fifteen hours.
-Fifteen hours?

1289
01:31:46.882 --> 01:31:49.176
What are we gonna do
for 15 hours?

1290
01:31:55.724 --> 01:31:56.850
War...

1291
01:31:56.891 --> 01:32:00.103
Oh. hell. no! Stewardess!

1292
01:32:00.144 --> 01:32:01.020
What is it good for?

1293
01:32:01.062 --> 01:32:02.271
Stewardess. get me another seat!

1294
01:32:02.313 --> 01:32:04.857
Nothing...Listen to me. y'all!

1295
01:32:04.899 --> 01:32:06.108
Stewardess!

1296
01:32:11.446 --> 01:32:12.698
Action!

1297
01:32:15.325 --> 01:32:16.660
It broke.

1298
01:32:24.166 --> 01:32:26.335
Don't move! Don't smile!

1299
01:32:40.181 --> 01:32:43.059
What is this shit
about your daughter?

1300
01:32:43.100 --> 01:32:44.227
Fifty million dollars?

1301
01:32:44.268 --> 01:32:46.103
Who you think you got.
Kelsey Clinton?

1302
01:32:46.145 --> 01:32:47.271
Fifty million dollars?

1303
01:32:47.313 --> 01:32:49.857
Who you think you got.
Kelsey--What's the line?

1304
01:32:49.940 --> 01:32:51.066
Fifty million dollars?

1305
01:32:51.108 --> 01:32:53.276
Who you think you got--
Is it Chelsea or Kelsey?

1306
01:32:53.318 --> 01:32:54.444
Fifty million dollars?

1307
01:32:54.486 --> 01:32:55.904
Who you think you got.
Chelsea Carter?

1308
01:32:55.946 --> 01:32:57.238
Fifty million dollars?

1309
01:32:57.280 --> 01:33:00.241
Who you think you got.
Chelsea Grammer--Chelsea--

1310
01:33:00.283 --> 01:33:02.160
Who do you think you got.
Chelsea Clinton?

1311
01:33:02.201 --> 01:33:03.327
Fifty million dollars?

1312
01:33:03.369 --> 01:33:05.413
Who you think you got.
Chelsea Clinton?

1313
01:33:05.454 --> 01:33:06.747
Keep him talking--

1314
01:33:06.789 --> 01:33:08.749
Cut! Go back to the beginning.

1315
01:33:08.791 --> 01:33:11.001
Was that it. Chelsea--
Did I get it?

1316
01:33:14.880 --> 01:33:16.047
Action!

1317
01:33:38.026 --> 01:33:40.987
All right. let me
see your badge. buddy!

1318
01:33:41.029 --> 01:33:43.489
No joke! Show your ass!

1319
01:33:43.531 --> 01:33:47.117
Show your ass? Y'all scared--

1320
01:33:47.159 --> 01:33:48.369
Cut!

1321
01:33:49.286 --> 01:33:52.289
You know that other stuff.
but don't know his name?

1322
01:33:52.331 --> 01:33:55.333
Man. people tell me shit.

1323
01:33:57.335 --> 01:33:58.753
What's wrong with you?

1324
01:34:01.339 --> 01:34:03.758
My daddy once caught--
catch a bullet--

1325
01:34:03.799 --> 01:34:05.634
caught a bullet--
catch a bullet--

1326
01:34:05.676 --> 01:34:06.802
caught a bullet.

1327
01:34:06.844 --> 01:34:10.431
My daddy one caught a bullet
by his bare hand.

1328
01:34:10.472 --> 01:34:12.140
No bullshit.

1329
01:34:13.517 --> 01:34:15.519
What's the honor in that?

1330
01:34:15.519 --> 01:34:18.521
You believe your father
wasting his life...

1331
01:34:21.691 --> 01:34:23.651
They must not--

1332
01:34:23.693 --> 01:34:25.695
You're right. man.
Let's go tell them.

1333
01:34:27.196 --> 01:34:28.489
Anything goes wrong...

1334
01:34:28.530 --> 01:34:32.492
you bust in there.
act like you're LA--

1335
01:34:32.534 --> 01:34:34.327
He cannot speak English.

1336
01:34:34.369 --> 01:34:38.289
Man. this is cool.
Han sending us to Hong Kong.

1337
01:34:38.373 --> 01:34:39.874
What's that line?

1338
01:34:41.667 --> 01:34:43.628
May I offer you some peanuts?

1339
01:34:58.349 --> 01:35:01.894
See. how difficult is that?
My English?

1340
01:35:01.936 --> 01:35:05.064
He even cannot say three words.
Chinese.

1341
01:35:05.106 --> 01:35:06.440
You need some lunch?

1342
01:35:06.482 --> 01:35:08.442
I got it before. Jackie.

1343
